Name: vacrelid
Description: The table this entry is for

Name: enabled
Description: If false, this table will not be autovacuumed, except\n to prevent transaction ID wraparound

Name: vac_base_thresh
Description: Minimum number of modified tuples before vacuum

Name: vac_scale_factor
Description: Multiplier for reltuples\n to add to vac_base_thresh

Name: anl_base_thresh
Description: Minimum number of modified tuples before analyze

Name: anl_scale_factor
Description: Multiplier for reltuples\n to add to anl_base_thresh
